title: The Rock: Special Edition , 1996
description:
Synopsis
All of San Francisco is taken hostage when a vengeful General seizes control of Alcatraz Island, threatening to launch missiles loaded with deadly poison gas! With time running out, only a young FBI chemical weapons expert and a notorious Federal prisoner have the skills to penetrate the island fortress and defuse the lethal situation.


Director Michael Bay 
Cast Sean Conery, Nicolas Cage, Ed Harris, John Spencer, David Morse, William Forsythe, Michael Biehn, Vanessa Marcil, Tony Todd 
Length 120 min 
Distributor Buena Vista 
Discs 1 

Video Pal
2.35:1, 16:9 
Languages Dolby Digital 5.1: English, German, Spanish . Dolby Surround: Russian 

Subtitles English, French, Italian, Spanish, German, Portuguese, Swedish, Norwegian, Danish, Finnish, Icelandic, Hebrew, Estonian, English for deaf people 


Saludos
